                                "stop": 15.461,
                                "byte_start": 92062,
                                "byte_stop": 153920,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 79-1740, Ball against James, and in 80-317, University of Texas against Camenisch will each be announced by Justice Stewart."
